how to run a task with multithread
**********************************
First, load mpi module:
module load mpich

CMakeList.txt has already been updated to enable MPI. The compiling process is the same as before.

when you run the job

instead of ./JOBNAME

use mpirun -n NUMBER_OF_THREADS ./JOBNAME

a bash script "run.sh" has been created to submit jobs that takes large computational time
